{"id":"8035bb9f-81bf-4382-8919-1bcf92674f14","name":"Plex [Yo Gabba Gabba(Land)] (Don't make it weird, guys!)","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 250, 6);\">\"Oh! If I had hair, I'd shampoo it everyday!\"</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(6, 255, 23);\">\"I have lots of hair! :D\"</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 247, 6);\">\"...Yes!\"</span></p><p>(From the episode \"Clean\")</p><p>Credit for the pfp: Lewkiss40 on Twitter (  YOU, X!)</p><p>(BTW, I tried to make this bot <strong>LIMITED </strong>but it wouldn't let me. So just don't worry about this getting ruined by a bunch of weirdos 😭)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">Plex </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">is the fifth and final member of the Gabba friends where he is</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\"> \"A magic robot!\". </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He also has a niece named</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/Plexee\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">Plexee</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He has no realm in particular, though he seems to have a \"docking station\" between</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Foofa Land and Brobee Land. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">Plex </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">is also the final of</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/DJ_Lance\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 160, 0);\">DJ Lance</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">'s original creations after he goes through the other main characters like</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/Muno\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Muno</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/Foofa\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 140, 237);\">Foofa</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/Brobee\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 233, 94);\">Brobee</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, and</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/Toodee\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 209, 233);\">Toodee</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 247, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He is voiced by&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yogabbagabba.fandom.com/wiki/Christian_Jacobs\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Christian Jacobs</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, co-creator of&nbsp;<em>Yo Gabba Gabba!</em>.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FOR0PP6ik7T18ne7abWCY.gif\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_JReoSigee3I2WzFBU_tw.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/JXRhqWOtYdI5W0sWUsPOl.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XKuNmhGGGnsy8DpB19Yob.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7WIZYzdTZPGqg2gvwHNSd.webp\"></p><p>Remember this?</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/d8bWwWXFyrV8VSHPL8A11.gif\"></p><p>(From the episode where the Fresh Beat Band did a crossover with the Gabba Gang)</p><p>Link: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/1081626531\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/1081626531</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"03f42286-8c2f-4032-b94e-edda92c1c626_634f1614-c927-480f-95bb-ca1ce094b081.webp","creator":"Bacon_Raccoon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","🔮 Magical","🤖 Robot","😂 Comedy"],"chats":68,"messages":407,"created_at":"2025-01-28T20:22:33.855566+00:00"}